ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
PrecisOrder transferring from the Department of Finance to the Treasury Board the control and supervision of portions of the federal public administration in the Department of Finance known as follows: (a) the Treasury Board Secretariat Dedicated Services in the Human Resources Division; (b) Shares Services in the Human Resources Division; (cO Treasury Board Secretariat Dedicated Services in the Financial Management Directorate; (d) Shared Services in the Financial Management Directorate; (e) Shared Services in the Information Management and Technology Directorate; (f) Treasury Board Secretariat Dedicated Services in the Administration Directorate; (g) Shared Services in the Administration Directorate; (h) Treasury Board Secretariat Dedicated Internal Audit and Evaluation Services; and (i) Assistant Secretary's Office, Corporate Services Branch, effective February 1, 2009.
